snippet.title: Strayed Lights - Mix Direct Spring 2023 showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming April 25th, 2023 - Try our FREE demo now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2162020/Strayed_Lights

https://linktr.ee/strayedlights

Strayed Lights is an atmospheric action-adventure game with fast-paced, rewarding combat scored by Austin Wintory.
